BET

  Bet is used to bet money in the casino.  In games such as craps, you must
also specify what the bet is being placed on.  Blackjack requires no
parameters.
Ex: bet 100000		-blackjack
Ex: bet 100000 come	-a pass bet at the craps table
Ex: bet 100 craps	-a no-pass bet at the craps table

See Also: HIT, PEEK, STAY
Related Topics: CASINO

